(134, '\'Cát tặc\' ở Sài Gòn bị vây bắt', 'Cat-tac-o-sai-gon-bi-vay-bat', 'Phạm Hồng Thích, 40 tuổi, cùng đồng phạm lái ghe hút trộm cát trên sông Đồng Nai, khu vực TP Thủ Đức, bị cảnh sát vây bắt nên nhảy xuống nước bỏ trốn', '<p class=\"description\">Phạm Hồng Th&iacute;ch, 40 tuổi, c&ugrave;ng đồng phạm l&aacute;i ghe h&uacute;t trộm c&aacute;t tr&ecirc;n s&ocirc;ng Đồng Nai, khu vực TP Thủ Đức, bị cảnh s&aacute;t v&acirc;y bắt n&ecirc;n nhảy xuống nước bỏ trốn.</p>\r\n<article class=\"fck_detail \">\r\n<div>\r\n<div contenteditable=\"false\">\r\n<figure class=\"item_slide_show clearfix\">\r\n<div id=\"video_parent_357179\" class=\"box_embed_video_parent embed_video_new\" data-vcate=\"1003834\" data-vscate=\"1003869\" data-vscaten=\"Ph&aacute;p luật\" data-vid=\"357179\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-articleoriginal=\"4477830\" data-ads=\"0\" data-license=\"1\" data-duration=\"29\" data-brandsafe=\"0\" data-type=\"0\" data-play=\"1\" data-frame=\"\" data-aot=\"\" data-videoclassify=\"None\" data-initdom=\"1\" data-view=\"inview\" data-auto=\"1\" data-status=\"play\">\r\n<div id=\"embed_video_357179\" class=\"box_embed_video\">\r\n<div class=\"bg_overlay_small_unpin\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"bg_overlay_small\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"embed-container\">\r\n<div id=\"video-357179\">\r\n<div id=\"parser_player_357179\" class=\"media_content\">\r\n<div id=\"videoContainter_357179\" class=\"videoContainter\">\r\n<div id=\"media-video-357179\" class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin vjs-workinghover vjs-v7 vjs-controls-enabled vjs-has-started media-video-357179-dimensions vjs-paused vjs-ended vjs-user-inactive\" lang=\"vi\" role=\"region\" data-subtitle=\"0\" data-mode=\"240|360|480|720\" aria-label=\"Video Player\">\r\n<div class=\"vjs-text-track-display\" aria-live=\"off\" aria-atomic=\"true\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"vjs-loading-spinner\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"vjs-control-text\">Video Player is loading.</span></div>\r\n<button class=\"vjs-big-play-button\" title=